    "purpose": "Per-execution host runtime for the executor module. execution.rs defines ExecutionRuntime, the host-side remote runtime of an agent Execution that holds an Arc<ExecutionContext>, its execution SessionEvent channel endpoints, and an optional worker join handle, and exposes new, sender, and run. execution_context.rs defines ExecutionContext, mirroring the agent-side TaskContext with the ExecutionSignature and the shared agent SessionEvent sender. mod.rs is re-export wiring only; method bodies are panic-backed interface placeholders.",
